---
layout: default
---
<div class="home">
    <style scoped>
        {% assign image = site.header_feature_image | relative_url | split: '.' %}
        .call-out_img {
            background-image: url('{{ image | join: '.' }}');
        }
        {% if site.header_feature_image_responsive %}
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .call-out_img {
                background-image: url('{{ image[0] | append: '-medium.' | append: image[1] | default: image}}');
            }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 576px) {
            .call-out_img {
                background-image: url('{{ image[0] | append: '-small.' | append: image[1] }}');
            }
        }
        {% endif %}
        .call-out_img {
    text-align: center;
    height: 80vh; /* 화면의 80% */
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; /* 세로 중앙 */
    align-items: center;     /* 가로 중앙 */
    background-size: contain; /* cover 대신 contain: 전체 이미지 보이게 */
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
        .call-out_img h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .call-out_img h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .call-out_img p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
		
		.header-overlay {
			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
			color: white;
			text-align: center;
			text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
		}
    </style>

    <div id="main" class="call-out call-out_img">
        <h1>{{ site.header_text | default: "황주현" }}</h1>
        <h2>{{ site.header_subtitle | default: "Game Programmer" }}</h2>
        <p>{{ site.header_intro | default: "안녕하세요, 게임 프로그래머 황주현입니다. 3D/2D 혼합 환경의 엔진을 직접 제작하며 프로젝트를 진행하고 있습니다." }}</p>
    </div>
	
<section id="about" class="container" style="padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center;">
  <h2>About Me</h2>
  <p>게임 엔진 개발과 3D 그래픽스를 좋아하는 컴퓨터공학 전공 학생입니다.</p>

  <div class="cards" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px;">
    
    <div class="card" style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; width: 250px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3>Education</h3>
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; text-align: left;">
        <li>2021-2025: 컴퓨터공학 학사</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; width: 250px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3>Experience</h3>
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; text-align: left;">
        <li>2024: XYZ 게임사 인턴 6개월</li>
        <li>2023: ABC 게임 공모전 참여</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; width: 250px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3>Skills</h3>
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; text-align: left;">
        <li>C++ / OpenGL</li>
        <li>게임 엔진 개발</li>
        <li>3D 모델링 & 애니메이션</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
    {% capture _blog %}{% include blog/blog.liquid %}{% endcapture %}
    {{ _blog | split: " " | join: " "}}
</div>

